<div class="mt-5"></div>
  <div class="container row">
    <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2 col-sm-10 offset-sm-1">
      <div class="pledge-text">
        <p><strong> You have elected the <span id="plan"><em><%= @pledge.plan %></em></span> pay plan for your annual pledge of <%= number_to_currency(@pledge.amount) %>. That would be <%= @pledge.divisor %> payments of <span id="payThis"><%= number_to_currency((@pledge.pay_this.to_f)/100) %>.</p>
  
        <p class="mt-2">If these numbers are not correct, click "edit pledge" to make changes. If OK, click "Pay with Card." You will be taken to a secure website that handles credit and debit card payments St. Paul's.</p>
  
        <p class="mt-2"><strong>
          If your circumstances change or for any other reason you wish to edit or remove these settings you may do so at any time.</strong></p>
  
  
      <div class="text-center" max-width="400px">
      <%= button_to "Pay now", pledge_payment_path, method: :post, remote: true, params: {id: @pledge.id}, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg" %>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-5 mb-5"></div>

      <% if current_user == @pledge.user %>
      <%= link_to 'Edit', edit_pledge_path(@pledge) %> | 

      <%= link_to 'Cancel this pledge', new_pledge_path %>
      <% end %>
      </div>
  </div>